We recommended that:

Management require the AOs in the Municipal Treasurer’s Office to strictly comply with the timely remittance/deposit of their collections as provided in Section 29, Volume I of the Manual on the NGAS for LGUs. New stub of accountable forms must be issued to Collecting Clerks only when collections from prior stubs issued to them were already remitted in full;

