Direct the LDRRMO to prepare the annual LDRRMFIP detailing all the PPAs to be funded in accordance with COA Circular 2012-002 to ensure proper evaluation of the same;

Instruct the Municipal Accountant to transfer the unutilized balances of CYs 2016 and 2017 amounting to ₱4,201,796.50 from the Special Trust Fund to GF for other social services as prescribed in Section 21 of RA No. 10121. Also, advice the MDRRMC to prioritize the utilization of the unexpended balance of LDRRMF for CY 2018 to ensure that this fund is used for the intended purpose within the prescribed period; and 

Direct the Municipal Accountant, in coordination with the MDRRMO to regularly prepare every month the Report on the Sources and Utilization of LDRRMF using the prescribed format in COA Circular No. 2012-002 and submit such report on or before the 15th day after the end of the month through the LDRRMC and LDC to the Audit Team in compliance with the reportorial requirements of the aforementioned COA Circular.

