Utilize locally generated income to establish and create additional local economic enterprises that will generate more revenue for the LGU and at the same time provides work opportunities for the people of San Jacinto;
Provide the basis of the monthly rate of wages of Job Orders;
Justify the numbers of Clerks and Utility Workers; and
Justify why wages of Job Orders in various schools and barangays were charged to the General Fund of the LGU.

